    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sliding decorative doors or panels that are the sole entrance to a concealed area in a shoin-style building. The term literally means "sleeping-room fixture." May be used to refer to the doorways rather than the panels themselves. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
